<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Đặt hàng thành công</title>

<style>

body{
    font-family:Arial;
    background:#f5f5f5;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
}

.box{
    background:white;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

h2{
    color:#28a745;
}

a{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:20px;
    text-decoration:none;
    background:#007bff;
    color:white;
    padding:10px 20px;
    border-radius:6px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="box">

<h2>✅ Đặt hàng thành công!</h2>

<p>Cảm ơn bạn đã mua hàng.</p>

<a href="/">Tiếp tục mua sắm</a>

</div>

</body>
</html>